outputs.output_descr: Regulatory and coordination mechanism established for a GoI led sustainable national mine action programme to reduce the land mine and explosive remnants of war (ERW) impact in Iraq

Regulatory and coordination mechanism established for a GoI led sustainable national mine action programme to reduce the land mine and explosive remnants of war (ERW) impact in Iraq
Improved quality of life for victims and communities affected by the contamination

project_descr: To develop and enhance national operational capacity for clearance; mine risk education/community liaison and victim assistance in Iraq. It will consist of two distinct components; 1) clearance/mine risk education and 2) Victim Assistance
project_title: Operational and  Victim Assistance Capacity Development
